Novak Djokovic reached the Miami Open semi-finals after beating David Ferrer 7-5 6-5 . 
  The world No 1 will face John Isner in the final  . 
  Andy Murray will play Tomas Berdych in the other semi-final . 
  Serena Williams beat Simona Halep in three sets to reach the women's final . 
  Carla Suarez Navarro beat Andrea Petkovic 6-3 6-2 in the quarter-finals . 
 